Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
This sublease offers office space in the desirable Boca Clinic, featuring a soaring, skylit atrium lobby, and beautiful finishes.

Built in 1984, and renovated in 2005, the Boca Clinic building includes 75,690 SF of medical office space, under the banner of Boca Raton Regional Hospital, Baptist Health South Florida.

This office features a reception area, four exam rooms, two private offices, a nurses station, and an in-suite restroom.
